{"tid":851122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"用中國國旗做垃圾袋？ 官方：清潔工不是刻意","createTime":"2018-10-07T02:00:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T03:42:45.000Z","uid":20933,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3bfde018f1d04f1509b6d818005148f4ee4e8d91","tid":851122,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T02:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181006/large/1538820497_936f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181006%2Flarge%2F1538820497_936f.jpg&h=9797ebd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有微博網民於昨日曝料，指河北省保定市定興收費站，及京昆高速定興收費站，有人竟用國旗做麻袋裝垃圾，稱「國慶節看到這一幕，氣死人，誰來管管？」定興縣委宣傳部事後表示，據警方調查，高速服務區清潔員用舊國旗包裹雜物，事後國旗已被妥善收好。<br />\n<br />\n定興縣委宣傳部回應內地傳媒查詢時表示，事發於京昆高速定興西服務區，路過遊客拍到國旗被當麻袋裝雜物，將相片上傳網上。當地派出所立即調查，初步查明事件發生於5日下午1時左右，京昆高速定興西服務區清潔員賈某某、王某某，因收集的雜物無處盛放，便用了一面舊國旗包裹，放在服務區南側，事後國旗被妥善收好，目前案件正在進一步調查中。<br />\n<br />\n定興縣委宣傳部有關領導表示，此事應是因清潔員不懂得國旗的意義和有關法律責任而引起，但不是刻意為之。"},{"pid":"ea609d0f72df15eec721ed65e80ceaaa40440a57","tid":851122,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T02:00:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181006/58764525\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181006%2F58764525&d=VXAYx0S8Fq2ve3j0i6Iwn4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=1cdae2e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181006%2F58764525&h=0c1e6258\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181006/58764525</a>"},{"pid":"11bae8c9ba9bbc5e6f22852e19687655b076de52","tid":851122,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T02:02:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=